<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>CliniCare Dashboard Chat</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #f3f5f9;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    .app {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .sidebar {
      width: 210px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #375dcb 0%, #2d4fb1 100%);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 10px 16px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .logo-icon {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: white;
      color: #375dcb;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
    }

    .menu {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .menu a {
      display: block;
      padding: 12px 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #dbe5ff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    .menu a:hover,
    .menu a.active {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      color: white;
    }

    .logout {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      padding-top: 18px;
    }

    .logout a {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #dbe5ff;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .logout a:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      color: white;
    }

    .main {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .topbar {
      height: 56px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d9dee8;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 22px;
      padding: 0 26px;
    }

    .search-box {
      width: 290px;
      height: 34px;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 0 12px;
    }

    .search-box svg {
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .search-box input {
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      background: transparent;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
    }

    .user-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 22px 34px 30px;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .add-btn {
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 20px;
      background: #375dcb;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 15px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(55, 93, 203, 0.25);
    }

    .add-btn:hover {
      background: #2e52c2;
    }

    .cards {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e6ebf2;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      padding: 26px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .appointment-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .appointment-item {
      border: 1px solid #edf0f5;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px 18px;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #1f2937;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .empty-box {
      min-height: 170px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      color: #7b8495;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .chat-widget {
      position: fixed;
      right: 24px;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 500px;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .chat-header {
      height: 58px;
      background: #f3f3f3;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d9dde5;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .chat-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .chat-brand-icon {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 11px;
      background: #375dcb;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .chat-user {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .chat-body {
      padding: 12px 14px 0;
      background: white;
    }

    .chat-inner {
      border: 5px solid #2d86dc;
      border-bottom-width: 4px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      min-height: 430px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 18px 16px 10px;
    }

    .chat-messages {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      padding-right: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      max-height: 300px;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    .message {
      max-width: 82%;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px 18px 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }

    .message.bot {
      background: #d6d9df;
      color: #333;
      align-self: flex-start;
    }

    .message.user {
      background: #3754bf;
      color: white;
      align-self: flex-end;
    }

    .message-time {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .chat-input-area {
      border-top: 1px solid #d9dde5;
      padding-top: 16px;
    }

    .chat-input-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .chat-input {
      flex: 1;
      height: 34px;
      border: 1px solid #cfd5df;
      border-radius: 11px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      outline: none;
    }

    .chat-input::placeholder {
      color: #9aa1ac;
    }

    .send-btn {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #d1d5db;
      color: #111827;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 18px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .send-btn:hover {
      background: #c3c9d2;
    }

    .chat-note {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #8a909b;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1200px) {
      .chat-widget {
        width: 430px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .sidebar {
        display: none;
      }

      .chat-widget {
        position: static;
        width: calc(100% - 40px);
        margin: 20px auto 0;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .hero {
        text-align: left;
      }

      .add-btn {
        position: static;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }

      .cards {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div>
        <div class="logo">
          <div class="logo-icon">+</div>
          <div class="logo-text">CliniCare</div>
        </div>

        <ul class="menu">
          <li><a href="#" class="active">Trang chủ</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Quản lý lịch hẹn</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Quản lý khoa và bác sĩ</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Quản lý chat bot</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Cài đặt</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="logout">
        <a href="#">Đăng xuất</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="main">
      <div class="topbar">
        <div class="search-box">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7" stroke="#6b7280" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="20" y1="20" x2="16.5" y2="16.5" stroke="#6b7280" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
          <input type="text" placeholder="Tìm kiếm bác sĩ, chuyên khoa..." />
        </div>
        <div class="user-name">Nguyễn Gia Huy</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="hero">
          <h1>Xin chào, Abc</h1>
          <p>Tổng quan sức khỏe của bạn</p>

          <button class="add-btn">
            <span style="font-size: 20px;">+</span>
            <span>Thêm lịch hẹn</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="cards">
          <div class="card">
            <h2>Lịch hẹn hôm nay</h2>
            <div class="appointment-list">
              <div class="appointment-item">09:00 – Bác sĩ Minh (Tim mạch)</div>
              <div class="appointment-item">10:30 – Bác sĩ Lan (Da liễu)</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2>Lịch đã hủy hôm nay</h2>
            <div class="empty-box">Không có lịch nào bị hủy</div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h2>Lịch hẹn sắp tới</h2>
            <div class="appointment-list">
              <div class="appointment-item">Ngày mai – 14:00 – Bác sĩ Nam</div>
              <div class="appointment-item">25/03 – 09:00 – Bác sĩ Hương</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <section class="chat-widget">
      <div class="chat-header">
        <div class="chat-brand">
          <div class="chat-brand-icon">+</div>
          <span>CliniCare</span>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-user">Nguyễn Gia Huy</div>
      </div>

      <div class="chat-body">
        <div class="chat-inner">
          <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
            <div class="message bot">
              Xin chào, Tôi là AI hỗ trợ y tế. Bạn đang gặp vấn đề gì?
              <div class="message-time">12:40 PM</div>
            </div>

            <div class="message user">
              Tôi bị đau đầu thường xuyên.
              <div class="message-time">12:41 PM</div>
            </div>

            <div class="message bot">
              Đau đầu thường xuyên có thể liên quan đến thiếu ngủ, căng thẳng hoặc vấn đề thần kinh.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="chat-input-area">
            <div class="chat-input-wrap">
              <input
                id="chatInput"
                class="chat-input"
                type="text"
                placeholder="Mô tả triệu chứng của bạn ..."
              />
              <button class="send-btn" onclick="sendMessage()">➤</button>
            </div>

            <div class="chat-note">
              ⚠ Đây là tư vấn sơ bộ. Vui lòng khám bác sĩ để chẩn đoán chính xác.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
